  "text": "The reporter vector used to assay thyroid hormone receptor activation and the expression vector for the rat thyroid hormone receptor TRa1 were as previously described [CITATION_1] . The reporter vectors for GR, PPARc and VDR, and the expression vectors for the rat GR, human PPARc and human VDR were gifts from Drs. C. Caelles, D. Haro and A. Aranda, respectively.",
